const LockIcon = () => (
  <svg
    xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
    width="24"
    height="24"
    viewBox="0 0 24 24"
    fill="none"
    stroke="currentColor"
    strokeWidth="2"
    strokeLinecap="round"
    strokeLinejoin="round"
    className="icon"
  >
    <rect width="18" height="11" x="3" y="11" rx="2" ry="2"></rect>
    <path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0 1 10 0v4"></path>
    <circle cx="12" cy="16" r="1"></circle>
  </svg>
)

export default LockIcon
